The paper deals with signal recovery on graphs using compressed sensing techniques and graph Fourier analysis. This suggests that the paper could belong to several sub-categories such as Information Theory (cs.IT), Social and Information Networks (cs.SI), Machine Learning (cs.LG), Data Structures and Algorithms (cs.DS), and Numerical Analysis (cs.NA). However, since the paper focuses on signal recovery, we can eliminate cs.SI and cs.LG as they are more concerned with network analysis and machine learning respectively. Additionally, since the paper involves numerical experiments, cs.NA is also a likely sub-category. Therefore, the most likely sub-categories are cs.IT and cs.DS, followed by cs.NA.
